Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來已經沒有什麼需要我再教了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫長的旅途 讓你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就到城鎮了 蜜爾佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.01,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}想要見你 卻覓不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:33.27,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}思念越發強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:37.39,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}無法傳達到這份祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:43.98,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}一定是因為	迷失了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:51.70,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}無論何時  只有被映在這眼瞳裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.16,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}是唯一的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:58.33,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}一直如此堅信著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.50,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}世界並非唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:06.26,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}還有所謂如果的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:10.26,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}因為存在著無限可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:15.89,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}正迷失著方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:19.65,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}想要見你 卻覓不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:21.65,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}不論你現在身處何處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:24.86,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}必定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:30.53,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}不慎闖入了瞳中的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.20,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:36.45,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被黑暗之手遮蔽了去路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:40.58,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被怯弱的心所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:42.38,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}也不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:46.96,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}繼續尋找著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.01,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:33.27,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}思いつのるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:37.39,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}この祈りが届かないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:43.98,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}何かをきっと 見失ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:51.70,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}いつだって この瞳に 映されたものだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.16,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}唯一の真実だと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:58.33,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}信じていたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.50,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}世界は一つじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:06.26,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}もしもという世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:10.26,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}無限にあるとして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:15.89,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}いま途方に暮れている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:19.65,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:21.65,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}いま何処にいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:24.86,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}必ず見つけ出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:30.53,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}迷い込んだのは瞳の中にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.20,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:36.45,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}例え暗闇がゆく手を遮り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:40.58,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}弱気な心惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:42.38,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}諦めないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:46.96,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}探しつづけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\fad(1200,1200)\be1\bord2\4a&Hc1&\3a&Hc1&\shad3\pos(505,372)}蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著 讓我們去看一看下一本書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來在這個世界裏 好像發生過一點不幸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭絲加勒絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 戴上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛 蘭絲加勒絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭絲加勒絲 你去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初美會在這種小島上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小啊 是無人島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那來這裡不是毫無意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 我先去偵察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剩我們兩人了呢 葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別發出那種怪聲 噁心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快累趴下了 不減肥不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊啊 你最好稍微減減肥 跟我一起去如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重啊 好重 真的好重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好重啊 果然是重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻鸚鵡全身的皮下脂肪高達100%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想變成大胖子的話最好停手喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 快停手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭絲加勒絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這隻虎是你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我是莉莉絲 這位是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 你們要打蜜爾佳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會做那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要欺負蜜爾佳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會欺負你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳住在這個島上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在島上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟誰一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞倫是蜜爾佳的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 像是在哪裡聽到過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 莉莉絲也是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成為你的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼想成為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說做朋友什麼的 只會吃虧所以讓人討厭的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了 是婆婆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個婆婆也是這個島上的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 以前在這個島上 現在不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 葉月是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼 剛才的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的是「啪哩啪哩」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啪哩啪哩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 「啪哩啪哩」是會稍微有點痛的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 塞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳大人 您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳今天也是沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾位是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們想和蜜爾佳成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以和他們成為朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 難得各位來拜訪這個小島
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我作嚮導帶領各位去行宮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 葉月有戀人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要長大後就會有戀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的戀人就是指男人 塞倫是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳從沒見過男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉月見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 見過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說男人都是很美妙的 是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉月是男人還是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 是女人 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人的奶子不會鼓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說葉月不是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣說很容易懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶子是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是乳房 關西腔裏叫奶子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳胸部沒有鼓起來 蜜爾佳是男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等蜜爾佳長到這麼大時 就會變成「波波」的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時男人就會一個接一個追著你跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結婚對像什麼的可以隨你挑選
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:09:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好喝 真是好茶葉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道真的不記得我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那頂帽子 還是讓人感到不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭絲加勒絲 重新向葉月打聲招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是那樣 那個孩子也真是古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是厲害 你是能夠明白的呢 蜜爾佳大人的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為蜜爾佳大人一直沒有長大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有長大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳大人從很多年以前開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個樣子沒有改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我之前負責教育蜜爾佳大人的人非常嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎每天都會很嚴厲地責罰蜜爾佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那樣不知持續了多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為蜜爾佳大人一直保持著小孩子的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人後來去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從一個年老的婆婆那裡聽到過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某一天 一件慘不忍睹的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個可怕的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事蜜爾佳知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像吃點心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果烤餅也可以的話 我可以做給你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 蜜爾佳好想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼帶我去廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好聞的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉月 你當我家裏的廚師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真正好吃的烤餅並不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經收到過全宇宙第一好吃的烤餅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 那個人就是葉月的戀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為葉月說話時目光非常的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以蜜爾佳就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天來的真是一些不可思議的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭絲加勒絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 莉莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結婚是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳大人 從哪裡聽到那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊那個古怪的鳥先生說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰是古怪的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就是跟男人卿卿我我 然後一直在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 就是這樣 到了晚上 慢慢地 慢慢地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等蜜爾佳長大後 一定會有一個美好的婚姻的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳能長大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一定能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 得想辦法先解決那個莫名其妙的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 蜜爾佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在睡覺之前要先洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大家一起去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好啊 一起去吧一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼 幹什麼 這種處置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底對我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣呢 葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得這麼一次 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 稍後我一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不用這麼害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉絲會去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說要在浴池裏 幫我教蜜爾佳大人從1數到100嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 去洗澡的話要脫掉那個帽子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是 要脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是讓人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「啪哩啪哩」的原因我已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 蜜爾佳 去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳已經脫完了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我的衣服脫起來比較費勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這種時候卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你是怎麼到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說都是靠毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個倒是有件好事情想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你是想去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接在這裡把禮服脫掉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 這樣觸碰人家的背會讓人家有感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是莉莉絲還是葉月還是塞倫胸部都好大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有蜜爾佳胸部平平的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無須擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人不只是胸部而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳今晚可以跟葉月一起睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 葉月的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那個人可以從葉月這裡得到很多的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻沒有人給蜜爾佳很多的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒我 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天蜜爾佳違反了囑咐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天蜜爾佳說了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天蜜爾佳頂了嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天蜜爾佳在心裏面說了「婆婆去死」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9436
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9545
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9654
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9763
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9872
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9981
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 完成的非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於沒有一個錯誤 可以給一些獎勵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 想要什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳想要一個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一個戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話蜜爾佳就可以得到很多的關心 變得很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的 你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為使用了魔力而讓成長停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是隨便說說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉月是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遠 很遠的國家來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪個國家裏有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼東西都有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是全都非常無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡大概有多少人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多得讓人討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人跟女人都有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉月為何沒跟戀人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在了 所以我正在找他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳也想去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳的戀人在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在這個海的對面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小黑鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的「啪哩啪哩」比以往都要長 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小黑鬼 停手 快停手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳要去海的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:41.45,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}永遠の祈りをささげて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:48.17,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}大事なもの諦めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:59.09,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}どんなに遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:02.47,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}きっと捕まえてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:10.23,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}君と僕との それが約束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:17.28,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}思いでも 抱きしめないでいても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:24.70,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}気持ちは 一つも届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:33.09,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}永遠お祈りをささげて
